<i>So the ring was for Itagaki-san.</i>

16
00:01:37,080 --> 00:01:39,060
You remembered everything, right?

17
00:01:41,710 --> 00:01:43,750
Including the accident?

18
00:01:43,750 --> 00:01:46,020
Not about the accident.

19
00:01:46,020 --> 00:01:49,790
I see. Then you should remain alert.

20
00:01:49,790 --> 00:01:52,140
If anything happens, call me...

21
00:01:53,180 --> 00:01:55,420
No, I guess you have Itagaki-san now.

22
00:01:57,260 --> 00:01:58,620
Kotaro-san, I-

23
00:01:58,620 --> 00:02:03,380
I really went overboard by calling myself your ex. Sorry.

24
00:02:03,380 --> 00:02:04,760
That's not true.

25
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:09,060
I was able to come this far, thanks to you.

26
00:02:09,060 --> 00:02:13,860
<i>Your saying I was being myself when I quit my job</i>

27
00:02:13,860 --> 00:02:17,240
